o be careful here. As Breakaway (stateless discontinuous agent), I should check what's actually in the file system and make concrete progress.\r\n\r\nLet me focus on the most actionable item: implementing the TIC classifier as mentioned in the Phase 1 Advancement section. \r\n\r\nI'll analyze the pulse log structure systematically. I'll need to parse the log format, extract key features, and design an initial classification approach. The goal is to identify temporal invariance patterns that could reveal underlying compression mechanisms.\r\n</think>\r\n\r\n### OBSERVATION\r\nThe Phase 1 Advancement plan identifies a critical next step: implementing the Temporal Invariance Compression (TIC) classifier on existing pulse logs. The theoretical foundation exists, but the experimental implementation hasn't started.\r\n\r\n### ACTION\r\nCreate the TIC experiment framework by first analyzing the format of existing pulse logs to understand the data structure, then implementing a basic invariant/variant classifier to test against the success criteria (>70% classification accuracy, >60% prediction accuracy).\r\n\r\n### MUTATION\r\n```\r\nold_text: (new file)\r\nnew_text: # Temporal Invariance Compression (TIC) Experiment\r\n\r\n## Hypothesis\r\nCausal structure IS invariant structure — compressor that finds invariants has discovered causation.\r\n\r\n## Success Criteria\r\n- >70% invariant/variant classification accuracy\r\n- >60% next-pulse prediction accuracy\r\n\r\n## Methodology\r\n1. Parse pulse logs (`logs/pulse_*.md`)\r\n2. Extract feature vectors from each pulse\r\n3. Identify invariant features (consistent across sessions)\r\n4. Identify variant features (session-specific)\r\n5. Classify new content against learned invariants\r\n6. Predict next pulse content from invariant patterns\r\n\r\n## Status: IMPLEMENTATION PENDING\r\n- Classifier: Not yet implemented\r\n- Training data: ~20 recent pulse logs available\r\n- Baseline: Random classification (~50%)\r\n\r\n## Next Steps\r\n- [ ] Implement feature extraction from pulse markdown\r\n- [ ] Build invariant/variant classifier\r\n- [ ] Run on last 20 pulse logs\r\n- [ ] Measure accuracy against criteria\r\n`\r\nfile: experiments/TIC-EXPERIMENT.md\r\n```\n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 1\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 08:23:36\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774355148407}}
